Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.60,0:02:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)\an5\pos(416,341)\fs26\i1\bord2\1c&H1512cc\3c&Hcccef2}困惑的“Flamehaze”
